Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.20,0:01:44.94,Main Dialog,Tokie,0000,0000,0000,,A Christmas party?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.94,0:01:46.41,Main Dialog,Girl A,0000,0000,0000,,And we can go, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.41,0:01:48.62,Main Dialog,Maruo,0000,0000,0000,,Of course. It's next Sunday.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.62,0:01:50.33,Main Dialog,Girls A-B-C-D,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.33,0:01:53.26,Main Dialog,Tokie,0000,0000,0000,,Since it's an Olympus party, will you play guitar for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.04,0:01:56.51,Main Dialog,Maruo,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if you've got a request...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.57,0:01:59.18,Main Dialog,Tokie,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ricchan, are you coming too?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.18,0:02:00.75,Main Dialog,Tokie,0000,0000,0000,,A Christmas party!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.58,0:02:03.89,Main Dialog,Tokie,0000,0000,0000,,You can go with Nishimi-san, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.30,0:02:08.61,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not really part of that group, so I'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.61,0:02:14.45,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, there's a Christmas mass at the church on Sunday.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.83,0:02:17.22,Main Dialog,Maruo,0000,0000,0000,,Then Kawabuchi-kun is going to that, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.22,0:02:18.00,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.68,0:02:20.31,Main Dialog,Maruo,0000,0000,0000,,We should've checked before...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.78,0:02:22.03,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Maruo-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.03,0:02:25.20,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't mind, I think I'd like to go to the party after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.74,0:02:26.71,Main Dialog,Maruo,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.71,0:02:28.93,Main Dialog,Maruo,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, you're very welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.93,0:02:31.71,Background Dialog,Maruo,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought you'd agree to come, Nishimi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.79,0:02:33.78,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Like this, little by little, it's best to put some distance between us.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.83,0:02:34.90,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sure of it...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.64,0:02:40.76,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.76,0:02:43.18,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,You're late, Bon-baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.18,0:02:45.68,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hi...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.68,0:02:48.44,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Next we'll play the Spiders.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.44,0:02:49.73,Main Dialog,Yamaoka,0000,0000,0000,,What about the Beatles?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.73,0:02:52.19,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go with "Bang Bang Bang"!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.93,0:03:03.10,Main Dialog,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Nishimi-san, how about some cider?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.37,0:03:04.27,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.69,0:03:10.12,Songs,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Feigning innocence, bang bang bang!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.50,0:03:15.41,Songs,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Bang bang, bababababababa-bang!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.60,0:03:20.60,Songs,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,He's someone I can't beat!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.67,0:03:25.10,Songs,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Bang bang, bababababababa-bang!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.10,0:03:28.04,Main Dialog,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Nishimi-san, let's sing together!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.44,0:03:31.31,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really know the popular songs...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.03,0:03:39.89,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wonder what {\i0}he's{\i1} doing right now...{\i0} 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.64,0:03:44.33,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Maybe he's talking to Ricchan at the church?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.73,0:04:12.00,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I go to a party and all I do is think about those two...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.34,0:04:14.28,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I feel like a fool...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.59,0:04:16.23,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.98,0:04:18.15,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Ricchan...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.65,0:04:20.03,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.03,0:04:21.45,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were going to church...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.25,0:04:23.45,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.45,0:04:26.63,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,The church's Christmas mass is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.45,0:04:30.41,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,He isn't here with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.96,0:04:33.71,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Does he have to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.60,0:04:36.92,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.92,0:04:39.34,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,He went home with the little ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.75,0:04:41.31,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.24,0:04:44.34,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,It's cold, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.34,0:04:45.35,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.62,0:04:48.06,Main Dialog,Sailor,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.60,0:04:50.02,Main Dialog,Sailor,0000,0000,0000,,I got you, babe!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.98,0:05:08.71,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, it's almost his birthday, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.56,0:05:12.01,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you finish in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.59,0:05:14.50,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.54,0:05:17.25,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you say things like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.06,0:05:19.00,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.34,0:05:20.28,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,This is for...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.62,0:05:24.34,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind! Kaoru-san, you're an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.51,0:05:31.68,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What did I do this time?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.69,0:05:33.88,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't know.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.33,0:05:37.19,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's hard to understand women.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.45,0:05:42.82,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why did I lose my temper like that?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.19,0:05:48.16,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm the one who rejected Kaoru-san in the first place.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.26,0:05:52.24,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if I finished knitting this,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.78,0:05:54.68,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}there's no way I'd be able to give it to him.{\i0} 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.60,0:06:26.18,Main Dialog,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I'm relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.18,0:06:28.65,Main Dialog,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,You're safe for now Yurika,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.65,0:06:30.87,Main Dialog,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,but let me tell you something...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.87,0:06:31.99,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.46,0:06:34.37,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to tell me not to see him, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.37,0:06:36.50,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to keep repeating yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.50,0:06:38.08,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Chet...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.08,0:06:39.16,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.08,0:06:41.18,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Chet!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.97,0:06:53.97,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Sentaro...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.27,0:06:55.73,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.22,0:06:57.56,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,What am I...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.56,0:06:59.48,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waitin' for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.48,0:07:03.26,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,W-Why are you acting so formal?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.48,0:07:08.55,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Rikko...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.13,0:07:12.32,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.21,0:07:17.61,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I never realized how you felt 'til now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.61,0:07:22.62,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I may have said dumb things an' hurt you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.27,0:07:24.25,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.25,0:07:27.47,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,But... um... how can I put it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.41,0:07:31.74,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,But about your feelings, I, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.94,0:07:43.73,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Sentaro, why are you suddenly on your best behavior?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.04,0:07:45.56,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it already.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.56,0:07:47.67,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't a yakuza movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.74,0:07:49.97,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Did I get it wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.74,0:07:54.75,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.41,0:07:56.33,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,You got it wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.82,0:08:01.08,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh, a misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.08,0:08:03.02,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for talkin' so weird...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.02,0:08:06.34,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right! We're like family.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.34,0:08:07.76,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,You made me nervous for a second there... 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.89,0:08:12.12,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I-In that case, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.10,0:08:15.84,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,We're like family,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.84,0:08:20.21,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,so I couldn't stand the thought of causin' you pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.42,0:08:29.22,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad I heard this now, and not a while back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.95,0:08:32.17,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.32,0:08:36.46,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm never going to tell a blockhead like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.13,0:08:49.67,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I have to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.58,0:08:53.43,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going back to Tokyo soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.60,0:09:00.10,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,I probably won't see you again...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.41,0:09:06.31,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,An upperclassman from my college
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.31,0:09:08.08,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,, is starting up his own publishing company
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.08,0:09:10.07,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,and he wants me to help him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.97,0:09:13.53,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,I plan on leaving soon after New Year's.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.23,0:09:17.03,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,It's taken me a long time to get to this point,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.03,0:09:20.03,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,but I owe it to you for making me think I should give going back another try.{try to shorten}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.46,0:09:21.84,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,I'm grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.14,0:09:26.48,Main Dialog,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Idiot. I don't want to hear those words.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.48,0:09:28.59,Main Dialog,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just don't leave me..."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.00,0:09:32.34,Main Dialog,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I couldn't bring myself to say it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.88,0:09:36.55,Main Dialog,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Not when he's finally trying to move forward.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.10,0:09:42.56,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Ritsuko-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.80,0:09:45.16,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Yurika-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.16,0:09:47.26,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,W-What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.26,0:09:48.48,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Looking for something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.90,0:09:52.24,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I carelessly threw something away that was important to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.91,0:09:55.15,Main Dialog,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, is that girl homeless?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.15,0:09:56.44,Main Dialog,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Ritsuko-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.94,0:09:59.50,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind me. Please, go on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.50,0:10:03.81,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,A beautiful girl like you shouldn't be seen doing something like this, Yurika-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.84,0:10:06.88,Main Dialog,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,Ritsuko-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.90,0:10:11.98,Main Dialog,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.06,0:10:17.06,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please, don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.06,0:10:18.43,Main Dialog,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,It's something important, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.93,0:10:21.43,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Yurika-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.79,0:10:24.55,Main Dialog,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,So... what am I looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.36,0:10:29.44,Main Dialog,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,Here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.44,0:10:30.54,Main Dialog,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,This is it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.54,0:10:31.57,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.55,0:10:36.07,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,But, I'll have to start over with clean yarn...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.07,0:10:38.70,Main Dialog,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,Is this going to be a present for someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.70,0:10:40.86,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Um... maybe.{added the maybe and extended the line-tweak it if you like}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.87,0:10:44.25,Main Dialog,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you throw away something so important?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.04,0:10:51.50,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I was confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.19,0:10:58.38,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I suddenly felt stupid for knitting a gift that I'd never be able to give.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.60,0:11:00.38,Main Dialog,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,Why wouldn't you be able to?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.38,0:11:04.43,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,B-Because a lot of things have happened between us...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.43,0:11:07.36,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,...and I once hurt him terribly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.36,0:11:08.60,Main Dialog,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,You turned him down, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.06,0:11:11.52,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,And I couldn't tell him I like him now, after all that,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.52,0:11:12.97,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,so I decided to let it go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.86,0:11:16.53,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,But then I thought that wouldn't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.33,0:11:22.40,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,See, there was another time when I said nothing and just gave up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.63,0:11:25.25,Main Dialog,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,Do you regret it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.25,0:11:30.31,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,No. I'd given up on that long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.72,0:11:33.94,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I've realized this person has been there
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.94,0:11:37.69,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,to support me all this time, whenever I've felt down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.49,0:11:43.43,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I had no confidence in myself, but he did his best to encourage me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.19,0:11:46.99,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,This time, I want to be the one to tell him how I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.11,0:11:52.13,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I finally decided to stop keeping my mouth shut and waiting for things to end.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.42,0:11:59.61,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for talking about this...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.61,0:12:02.14,Main Dialog,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm glad you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.82,0:12:04.72,Main Dialog,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,I think you've opened my eyes as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.28,0:12:07.45,Main Dialog,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.45,0:12:09.39,Main Dialog,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.39,0:12:10.91,Main Dialog,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,Who's your prince, Ritsuko-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.91,0:12:12.86,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.45,0:12:14.96,Main Dialog,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I try and guess?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.96,0:12:17.04,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,W-W-What are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.04,0:12:18.22,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Please, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.85,0:12:20.32,Main Dialog,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,You're so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.44,0:12:34.74,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I'm set to leave this weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.91,0:12:39.61,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Working in Tokyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.61,0:12:40.73,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.73,0:12:43.43,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,A lot happened at college and I ended up dropping out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.62,0:12:47.66,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,But you'll come back once in a while, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.66,0:12:49.12,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Like you've been doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.33,0:12:52.48,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,No. I'm never coming back to this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.33,0:12:57.53,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru-kun, our sessions were fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.84,0:12:59.86,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,I'll miss seeing you and Sen-bou,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.86,0:13:02.19,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,but I don't want you guys to stop playing jazz.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.70,0:13:04.01,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Jun-nii-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.01,0:13:06.83,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Did you tell him you were going back to Tokyo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.36,0:13:14.60,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sen!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.61,0:13:18.12,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,What's the hubbub, Bon?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.91,0:13:21.38,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,It's about Jun nii-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.38,0:13:24.31,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, he's about to go back to Tokyo, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.31,0:13:25.82,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I heard from Pops.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.00,0:13:29.32,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Well, ain't got nothin' to do with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.32,0:13:32.29,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wanna jam?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.29,0:13:34.92,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to let that be the last you see of him?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.66,0:13:37.37,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothin' to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.29,0:13:42.01,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,You looked up to him as a big brother since you were a kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.49,0:13:46.52,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,You may never get the chance to meet him again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.52,0:13:48.10,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,There'd be no point.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.10,0:13:50.47,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Once he's gone, it'll be too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.68,0:13:54.16,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Enough about Jun-nii already.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.52,0:13:55.73,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get started here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.82,0:14:09.71,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't feel like practicin', I'm goin' home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.63,0:14:18.74,Main Dialog,Old Woman,0000,0000,0000,,What's all the fuss about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.74,0:14:23.09,Main Dialog,Man,0000,0000,0000,,I guess college students from Tokyo and all over have come to demonstrate
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.09,0:14:25.26,Main Dialog,Man,0000,0000,0000,,against letting the nuclear aircraft carrier into port.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.85,0:14:28.60,Main Dialog,Old Woman,0000,0000,0000,,That's terrible...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.56,0:14:32.47,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In their eyes, I'm a traitor.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.41,0:14:36.48,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They may never forgive me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.43,0:14:38.49,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.94,0:14:44.99,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...all I can do is search in my own way from now on.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.59,0:14:47.80,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Using a different method than them...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.42,0:14:59.88,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're here, Bon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.88,0:15:00.97,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Here, eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.35,0:15:03.88,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I made it myself, so it might be a little salty...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.88,0:15:06.35,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,But if you're not gonna eat it, I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.82,0:15:08.93,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Is this any time to be eating?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.34,0:15:11.85,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Did you forget what I said last time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.13,0:15:16.22,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talkin' about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.22,0:15:17.31,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Don't play dumb!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.31,0:15:19.43,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to be stubborn until it's too late?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.69,0:15:23.68,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Jun nii-san is leaving this town today or tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.06,0:15:25.16,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,It's today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.74,0:15:28.49,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,I'm taking the night train, Kaoru-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.58,0:15:35.24,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Sen-bou, this was rather old-fashioned of you.
