Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.24,0:15:37.27,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it was some kind of joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.27,0:15:39.10,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,It's no joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.10,0:15:42.54,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to try havin' a serious showdown with you, Jun-nii.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.95,0:15:48.05,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... You're not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.07,0:15:50.30,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I made it in time?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.30,0:15:51.74,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Let me in on it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.48,0:16:12.86,Background Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Musical Note: "Four" by Miles Davis
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.33,0:16:58.32,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is no duet.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.32,0:17:03.07,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They're seriously duking it out.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.20,0:17:30.30,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for causing you so much trouble, Pops.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.95,0:17:32.23,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.23,0:17:36.15,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,And when you reach Tokyo, first thing you do is get to a barber!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.27,0:17:38.54,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.73,0:17:41.41,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.27,0:17:45.37,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Jun-nii!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.84,0:17:49.13,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I'll remember today's session
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.79,0:17:52.15,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,for the rest of my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.77,0:17:55.65,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.28,0:17:58.23,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Me too, Sen-bou.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.42,0:18:14.28,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.28,0:18:16.59,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,I told you not to see me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.59,0:18:19.08,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,I have four questions I want you to answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.47,0:18:22.58,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,If you try to dodge me, I'll get on this train with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.71,0:18:25.33,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,So answer me truthfully.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.83,0:18:28.83,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Question number one:
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.83,0:18:30.81,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you tell me not to see you of{\fsp6}f?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.84,0:18:35.43,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,I hate sad goodbye scenes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.84,0:18:37.55,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Question number two:
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.55,0:18:40.23,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you think to take me with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.15,0:18:44.42,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,The work I'm going to be doing is kind of a gamble.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.42,0:18:47.45,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I took you, there's no \Nguarantee of making any kind of living.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.76,0:18:50.42,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, you're still in high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.42,0:18:51.86,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Question number three...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.87,0:18:56.30,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you do anything more than kiss me?! 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.74,0:19:01.26,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Did you not touch me because you intended to leave from the start?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.89,0:19:05.75,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.52,0:19:08.16,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,I knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.16,0:19:10.75,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,I knew how much you cared about me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.19,0:19:15.51,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,This is my last question...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.40,0:19:20.16,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Won't you take me with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.04,0:19:25.52,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to take good care of your own life.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.53,0:19:36.80,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,I figured you would say something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.53,0:19:40.53,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Now it feels like I've been set free, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.07,0:19:44.05,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going back to my own world.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.08,0:19:47.54,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Junichi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.57,0:19:49.54,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.29,0:19:53.67,Main Dialog,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Yurika, where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.67,0:19:55.55,Main Dialog,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Come out, Yurika!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.85,0:19:58.09,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you embarrass us by walking out
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.09,0:20:00.04,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,in the middle of an arranged marriage meeting like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.04,0:20:01.55,Main Dialog,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, dear!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.55,0:20:04.06,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,We're going back there together, Yurika!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.56,0:20:09.06,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Yurika, where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.95,0:20:19.27,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm going back to my own world.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.26,0:20:42.77,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,I dragged you on board...{ ): snap...was I wromg...}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.27,0:20:45.50,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.77,0:20:48.68,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,What is there to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.68,0:20:50.53,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,The train's already left the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.53,0:20:51.77,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.56,0:20:56.39,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Well, when we get there, we'll go to my room first
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.77,0:20:59.78,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,and maybe I'll have you cut my hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.67,0:21:09.61,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,It's freezing today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.61,0:21:12.45,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Think I'll light the heater.
